    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    Matrix,
    lme4,
    carData,
    mlbench,
    ggplot2,
    mlmRev,
    testthat (>= 2.1.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
Imports: 
    bayesplot,
